graph TD
    Launch([Launch App]) --> Now
    Now[Now Tab<br/>当前行为]
    Timeline[Timeline Tab<br/>事件流]
    Review[Review Tab<br/>统计聚合]
    Events[Events Tab<br/>原始记录]

    Now <-->|tab| Timeline
    Timeline <-->|tab| Review
    Review <-->|tab| Events
    Events <-->|tab| Now

    Now --> Idle[Idle: Task 列表]
    Now --> Active[Active: 72sp 计时器]
    Idle -->|tap task| Active
    Active -->|stop| EventDB[(Event 持久化)]

    Timeline --> ByDay[按 Today/Yesterday/日期分组]

    Review --> Range[分段: Today / Week / Month / All]
    Range --> Bars[每 Task 总时长 + 条形 + 计数]

    Events --> Filter[过滤: All/Today/Week/With note]
    Events --> Edit[Edit Dialog: 改 Task / Note / 删除]
    Edit --> EventDB

    classDef tab fill:#F2F2F7,stroke:#5E6AD2,stroke-width:2px,color:#0A0A0A
    classDef screen fill:#FFFFFF,stroke:#6E6E73,color:#0A0A0A
    classDef storage fill:#5E6AD2,stroke:#5E6AD2,color:#FFFFFF
    class Now,Timeline,Review,Events tab
    class Idle,Active,ByDay,Range,Bars,Filter,Edit screen
    class EventDB storage
